<P>
   CONGRESS-COST _ WASHINGTON _ As fireworks etch the skies with
bright colors for the last Independence Day of this century, the
majestic dome of the U.S. Capitol will look much as it did 99 years
ago. But almost everything else about Capitol Hill has changed in a
century that brought an explosion of staff, construction and
bureaucracy _ not to mention lobbyists _ to Congress. (Malone, Cox
News Service). 20.
</P>
